              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Neutron capture cross-sections to form 242Cm were",
                "measured for all five irradiations. Total cross-",
                "sections for Am-241(n,g)Am-242g have been derived from",
                "these measurements and the measured branching ratio of",
                "Am-242g and assuming total destruction cross-section",
                "of 6000 barns to Am-242g."
